org.hibernate.ogm.datastore.infinispan.persistencestrategy.impl

Interface KeyProvider<EK,AK,ISK>

  • Type Parameters:
    EK - the entity cache key type
    AK - the association cache key type
    ISK - the identity source cache key type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OnePerKindKeyProvider, PerTableKeyProvider

    public interface KeyProvider<EK,AK,ISK>
    Converts the OGM-internal keys into the cache keys. Implementations must be thread-safe.
    Author:
    Emmanuel Bernard <emmanuel@hibernate.org>
